# Pocket Mint — Cline Rules
# Dibaca otomatis oleh Cline setiap sesi.

## Project Context
Monorepo expense tracker "Pocket Mint".
- Frontend : apps/frontend (Next.js App Router)
- Backend  : apps/backend (Express + Prisma)
- Database : Supabase PostgreSQL

## Design System Aktif: Pro-Fintech Dark
Referensi lengkap: apps/frontend/skills/design.md
JANGAN gunakan "Midnight Executive" (navy/cyan) —
bukan design system aktif.

Warna wajib dipakai:
  Background : #131313 (app), #0e0e0e (card), #0a0a0a (input)
  Surface    : #1c1b1b (elevated), #2a2a2a (highlight)
  Border     : #262626 (default), #3d4a3e (filled), #1a1a1a (divider)
  Text       : #e5e2e1 (primary), #bccabb (secondary), #3d4a3e (disabled)
  Primary    : #4ade80 (mint) — CTA, active, income
  Primary dim: #3ac070 | Primary bright: #6bfb9a
  Error/Debt : #ffb4ab — expense, debt, error
  Glow mint  : rgba(74,222,128,0.12)
  Glow error : rgba(255,180,171,0.12)

DILARANG: bg-slate-*, bg-gray-*, bg-zinc-*, bg-indigo-*,
          text-emerald-*, text-rose-*, border-slate-*, border-gray-*

